			<div class="col-sm-12 content-wrap">
				<p class="justify">The BUDOKON®MARTIAL ARTS style operate on a six-belt
system: White, Red , Blue , Purple , Brown , Black
Students start at the white belt level and continue through the ranks until black belt.
Each belt rank takes approximately 6 months to 1 year to achieve. Each belt is
measured by classroom &amp; personal practice hours and curriculum-specific exams.
Belt exams are held every three months giving students the opportunity to test for
their belt rank year-round.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

