			<div class="col-sm-12 content-wrap">
				<p class="justify">Under this pillar we learn to master yogic asana, martial arts standing &amp; ground
fighting (including striking, throws, and submissions), the Budokon animal series, and
much more. As students progress in belt rank they will build upon the base
knowledge they have learned from the previous belt.</p>
