	<div class="container section-content">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-12 content-wrap">
				<p class="justify">In this area of our curriculum we learn how our personal story (our perception of our life up to now) guides our daily emotions towards bio-chemical relationships we develop within our bodies and our addictions to these states and feelings. We learn a process of thought watching that allows us to identify emotion as a bio-chemical release based on a perception of reality that is controllable by shifting our language, beliefs, and our personal stories.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
