				<p class="justify">In this area of our curriculum we learn about our predetermined biological response
mechanisms and how they affect our relationships.We learn skills to better
communicate our needs and to understand the needs of others. We study language
and its effects on perception. We develop skills to be more tolerant and to contain our
emotions until they are further processed and understood.</p>
